text: Helmut Längle (born 29 September 1936) is an Austrian wrestler. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Austria Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vorarlberg Category:People from Feldkirch District
